➜双语故事 | On the bus
http://www.sohu.com/a/423070427_100171577	29908
<p class="ql-align-justify">The bus stops at the next stop. A mother and her child get on the bus and sit down. The conductor comes to them for the tickets. </p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">公交车到了下一站。一位母亲和她的孩子上了公共汽车，坐了下来。售票员让他们买票。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">The mother says, “One ticket to the Children’s Park.”</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">妈妈说，“一张去儿童公园的票。”</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">The conductor looks at the small child, then says to him, “How old are you, little boy?”</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">售票员看了看那个小孩，问他，“小朋友，你多大了？”</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">The mother wants to speak, but the conductor stops her.</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">那位妈妈想开口，但是售票员阻止了她。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">The boy says, “Mother says I’m four years old at home and two on the bus.”</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">那个男孩说，“妈妈说我在家四岁，在公交车上两岁。”</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">All the people laugh.</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">所有人都笑了。</p>
